-- Royal Dutch Refinery in Montreal Has `Release of Energy', Spokesman Says
-- B y   P a u l   B u r k h a r d t
-- 2010-10-15T16:20:45Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-15/royal-dutch-refinery-in-montreal-has-release-of-energy-spokesman-says.html
Royal Dutch Shell Plc had a
“release of energy” at its shut Montreal refinery in Canada,
said Larry Lalonde, a spokesman for the company. Two workers
were sent to the hospital to be checked out after the incident,
he said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
